trans-unit.source: Implements a markup extension that enables application authors to customize control styles based on the current system theme.
trans-unit.target: Implementerer filtypen markup som aktiverer programmet forfattere tilpasse stiler kontroll basert på gjeldende system tema.

trans-unit.source: This class is a markup extension implementation.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen er en markup utvidelsen implementering.

trans-unit.source: Markup extension classes exist mainly to provide infrastructure support for some aspect of the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation, and the members exposed by a markup extension are not typically called from user code.
trans-unit.target: Markup utvidelsen klassene finnes først og fremst for å gi infrastruktur støtte for deler av det [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering og medlemmer vises av filtypen markup ikke kalles fra brukerkode.

trans-unit.source: This extension supports the [ThemeDictionary Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) usage from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Denne utvidelsen støtter den [ThemeDictionary Markup utvidelsen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) Bruk fra [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] information, see [ThemeDictionary Markup Extension](../Topic/ThemeDictionary%20Markup%20Extension.md).
trans-unit.target: ## XAML tekst-Bruk For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] informasjon, se [ThemeDictionary Markup filtypen](../Topic/ThemeDictionary%20Markup%20Extension.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.ThemeDictionaryExtension"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.ThemeDictionaryExtension"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.ThemeDictionaryExtension"></xref> class, using the specified assembly name.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.ThemeDictionaryExtension"> </xref> class, ved hjelp av angitte samlingsnavnet.

trans-unit.source: The assembly name string.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen strengen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string setting a particular naming convention to identify which dictionary applies for a particular theme.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en streng som angir en bestemt navnekonvensjonen til å identifisere hvilke ordlisten gjelder for et bestemt tema.

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Text Usage For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] information, see [ThemeDictionary Markup Extension](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: ## XAML tekst-Bruk For [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] informasjon, se [ThemeDictionary Markup filtypen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: The assembly name string.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen strengen.

trans-unit.source: Returns an object that should be set on the property where this extension is applied.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer et objekt som skal angis for egenskapen der denne utvidelsen skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: For <xref href="System.Windows.ThemeDictionaryExtension"></xref>, this is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] value for a particular theme dictionary extension.
trans-unit.target: For <xref href="System.Windows.ThemeDictionaryExtension"> </xref>, dette er den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] verdien for en bestemt tema ordlisten filtype.

trans-unit.source: This method supports [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation, and is not intended to be called directly.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden støtter [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-winclient-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering og skal ikke kalles direkte.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] processor implementation uses this method for proper handling of `ThemeResourceDictionary` extension values during object creation.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] prosessor implementering bruker denne metoden for riktig behandling av `ThemeResourceDictionary` utvidelsen verdier under opprettelse av objekt.

trans-unit.source: This implementation relies on services based on the passed `serviceProvider`.
trans-unit.target: Denne implementeringen, avhengig av tjenester basert på den innsendte `serviceProvider`.

trans-unit.source: It must not be `null`.
trans-unit.target: Kan ikke være `null`.

trans-unit.source: The `serviceProvider` object is expected to implement <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IXamlTypeResolver>.
trans-unit.target: Den `serviceProvider` objektet er forventet å implementere <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IXamlTypeResolver>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.IXamlTypeResolver>

trans-unit.source: An object that can provide services for the markup extension.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som kan gi tjenester for markup filtypen.

trans-unit.source: This service is expected to provide results for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IXamlTypeResolver>.
trans-unit.target: Denne tjenesten er forventet å oppgi resultater for <xref:System.Windows.Markup.IXamlTypeResolver>.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.IXamlTypeResolver>

trans-unit.source: The object value to set on the property where the extension is applied.
trans-unit.target: Objektverdien for egenskapen der utvidelsen skal brukes.

trans-unit.target: Du må angi verdier for denne under konstruksjon eller før du bruker metoden ProvideValue.
